    RHODS -->|deploys all| TrainingOp
    RHODS -->|deploys all| CodeFlare
    RHODS -->|deploys all| KubeRay
    RHODS -->|deploys all| Kueue
    RHODS -->|deploys all| TrustyAI

    %% Dashboard Dependencies
    Dashboard -->|creates CRs| NotebookCtrl
    Dashboard -->|creates CRs| DSP
    Dashboard -->|creates CRs| KServe
    Dashboard -->|queries metrics| Prometheus
    Dashboard -->|API integration| ModelRegistry

    %% Notebook Dependencies
    NotebookCtrl -->|uses images| NotebookImages
    NotebookCtrl -->|routing| Istio
    NotebookImages -->|data access| S3
    NotebookImages -->|source code| Git
    NotebookImages -->|packages| PyPI

    %% KServe Dependencies (Critical Path)
    KServe -->|autoscaling| Knative
    KServe -->|traffic mgmt| Istio
    KServe -->|OpenShift integration| ModelCtrl
    KServe -->|model storage| S3
    KServe -->|metadata| ModelRegistry
    KServe -->|TLS certs| CertManager

    %% ModelMesh Dependencies
    ModelMesh -->|OpenShift integration| ModelCtrl
    ModelMesh -->|model storage| S3
    ModelMesh -->|inference monitoring| TrustyAI

    %% Model Controller Dependencies (Integration Hub)
    ModelCtrl -->|auth policies| Authorino
    ModelCtrl -->|VirtualServices| Istio
    ModelCtrl -->|ServiceMonitors| Prometheus

    %% Pipelines Dependencies
    DSP -->|model deployment| KServe
    DSP -->|artifact storage| S3
    DSP -->|metadata DB| ExternalDB
    DSP -->|model tracking| ModelRegistry

    %% Training Dependencies
    TrainingOp -->|workload queueing| Kueue
    TrainingOp -->|gang scheduling| SchedulerPlugins
    TrainingOp -->|gang scheduling| Volcano
    TrainingOp -->|training data| S3
    TrainingOp -->|checkpoints| S3

    %% CodeFlare Dependencies
    CodeFlare -->|Ray clusters| KubeRay
    CodeFlare -->|AppWrapper queueing| Kueue

    %% KubeRay Dependencies
    KubeRay -->|metrics| Prometheus

    %% Kueue Dependencies (Admission Hub)
    Kueue -->|admits| TrainingOp
    Kueue -->|admits| CodeFlare

    %% TrustyAI Dependencies
    TrustyAI -->|monitors| ModelMesh
    TrustyAI -->|monitors| KServe
    TrustyAI -->|metrics| Prometheus

    %% All Components to Platform
    RHODS -->|API calls| K8sAPI
    Dashboard -->|API calls| K8sAPI
    NotebookCtrl -->|API calls| K8sAPI
    KServe -->|API calls| K8sAPI
    ModelMesh -->|API calls| K8sAPI
    ModelCtrl -->|API calls| K8sAPI
    DSP -->|API calls| K8sAPI
    TrainingOp -->|API calls| K8sAPI
    CodeFlare -->|API calls| K8sAPI
    KubeRay -->|API calls| K8sAPI
    Kueue -->|API calls| K8sAPI
    TrustyAI -->|API calls| K8sAPI

    %% Image Dependencies
    RHODS -->|pulls images| Registries
    NotebookCtrl -->|pulls images| Registries
    KServe -->|pulls images| Registries
    ModelMesh -->|pulls images| Registries
    DSP -->|pulls images| Registries
    TrainingOp -->|pulls images| Registries

